(3995, 1, '2016-05-10 21:03:01', '2016-05-10 21:03:01', '<article>This is a wireframe for a potential iPhone app which I named “2 Plates”.  Check it out <a href="https://www.justinmind.com/usernote/tests/11448499/11448502/15247340/index.html">HERE</a>.The concept for this project was to design a wireframe for a CrossFit Companion which would help users keep track of milestones achieved during their workout sessions.  This app is a combination of multiple other apps that are available on the market, as well as containing features that aren’t immediately available on the app store.\r\n\r\nFor example, it has a tool which allows users to record themselves, and then have the ability to draw on the video.  This would be useful for showing weaknesses in a users form during a specific exercise.  Another tool allows users to setup competitions called “ThrowDowns”, and also keep track of the progress of the competition.\r\n\r\nThere are many more features of this app, and I think it does a good job of showing what is possible with a wire framing application.\r\n\r\n</article>\r\n<div class="socshare"></div>', '2Plates Interactive WireFrame', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '2plates-interactive-wireframe', '', '', '2016-05-10 21:08:53', '2016-05-10 21:08:53', '', 0, 'http://portfolio:8887/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=3995', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
