(4007, 1, '2016-05-10 21:22:09', '2016-05-10 21:22:09', 'One of the sites I worked on at my job was the University of Miami’s Points of Pride website.  This site details some of the achievements that the university has accumulated during the 2015 year.\r\n\r\nFeel free to head over to <a href="http://pride.miami.edu/">http://pride.miami.edu/</a> to check it out!\r\n\r\nFor this project, I got to work with a great designer (Brandon Wilson) and we came up with wireframes, and a whole over all concept for the site.\r\n\r\nEven though we had some troubles getting it going, once we got it working, all the effort really shined. So props to everyone at the office for getting this site up and running as quickly as  we were able to.', 'Points of Pride', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4002-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-10 21:22:09', '2016-05-10 21:22:09', '', 4002, 'http://portfolio:8887/2016/05/10/4002-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
